overview: Izzy has recently graduated from university and is on her way to LA to pursue her dreams of becoming an actress, but her plans are quickly derailed when she is left stranded at a gas station by her friends. With nothing more than her clothes in her luggage, she has to find her way to LA with the help of the gas station attendant, Seahawk. She spends the day in New Mexico, learning more about herself, her dreams and what it means to be an alien in the US.
title: Seahawk and the Thai Princess
